column2: SELECT TOP # star.apogee_id, star.ra, star.dec, star.l, star.b, star.glon, star.glat, star.vhelio_avg, star.vscatter, obj.j, obj.h, obj.k, obj.ak_targ, obj.ak_targ_method, obj.ak_wise, aspcap.teff, aspcap.logg, aspcap.param_m_h FROM apogeeStar star JOIN aspcapStar aspcap on aspcap.apstar_id = star.apstar_id JOIN apogeeObject obj on aspcap.target_id = obj.target_id WHERE (aspcap.aspcapflag & dbo.fApogeeAspcapFlag (#) ) = # and aspcap.teff > # and (star.vhelio_avg > #) and (star.starflag & dbo.fApogeeStarFlag (#) ) = # and star.nvisits > #
